; Regression test for issue #2948: lot annotations from {{total_price}}
; syntax must match those created by @@ syntax.
;
; When using {{£100}} to remove a lot whose cost was recorded via @@ £100,
; the per-unit price must be normalized to the same display precision in
; both code paths, otherwise the lots don't match and annotations leak
; into the balance report.

2025/09/04 * Broker
    Assets:Brokerage                       $123.45   @@ £100
    Assets:Brokerage                      -$123.45   {{£100}} [2025-09-04] @ $1
    Expenses:Finance:Fees                    $1.00
    Assets:Brokerage

test bal --lots
             $122.45
               £-100  Assets:Brokerage
               $1.00  Expenses:Finance:Fees
--------------------
             $123.45
               £-100
end test
